  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of PAC-14028 Cream in Pediatric Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Study to Investigate the Safety, Tolerability, Systemic Exposure and Efficacy of PAC-14028 in Children With Mild to Moderate Pediatric Atopic Dermatitis</official_title>
